      <abstract>
	The Debian META Manual gives an overview of all the manuals
	available within the Debian GNU/Linux distribution. This
	overview includes documentation written specifically for
	Debian GNU/Linux (as part of the Debian Documentation Project)
	as well as documentation written for Linux in general
	(e.g. various Linux magazines). 
      </abstract>

